execution_info.description: symmetric refers to the EOMs and means that no lateral analysis is done. simple refers to engine analysis, where approximate values are used
sfull refers to the EOMs and means that full analysis is done (lat and long). simple refers to engine analysis, where approximate values are used
symmetric refers to the EOMs and means that no lateral analysis is done. Lookup refers to engine performance maps, where exact values are looked up.
